      "text": {
        "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Problem\">Problem</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Problem\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Solve for <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/8/0/2/802813cb25bec0d5ac7c616c35a8592516a41e3e.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x \\in R$\" style=\"vertical-align: -1px\" width=\"46\" height=\"13\" />:\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/4/4/0/44072e3d8c42dcebd549b78ebec931171f53483b.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\[\\sin^3{x}(1+\\cot{x})+\\cos^3{x}(1+\\tan{x})=\\cos{2x}\\]\" width=\"349\" height=\"20\" />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Solution\">Solution</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Solution\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Let <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/6/9/c/69c1f9fe4e0998b28c45348eb3d744bfb2b0dd41.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a = \\sin{x}$\" width=\"69\" height=\"12\" /> and <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/5/0/9/5098f21d66bc7a839e9fbbd7eae34d50e25d57ba.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$b = \\cos{x}$\" width=\"69\" height=\"12\" />.  Substitution results in\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/c/f/5/cf5cc4232a7cca549c201ba355e724f74bb7fd24.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\begin{align*} a^3 (1 + \\frac{b}{a}) + b^3 (1 + \\frac{a}{b}) &amp;= b^2 - a^2 \\\\ a^3 + a^2b + ab^2 + b^3 &amp;= b^2 - a^2 \\\\ a^2 (a+b) + b^2 (a+b) &amp;= (b+a)(b-a) \\\\ (a+b)(a^2 + b^2 + a - b) &amp;= 0. \\end{align*}\" width=\"313\" height=\"119\" />\nBy the <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/Zero_Product_Property\" title=\"Zero Product Property\">Zero Product Property</a>, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/c/7/8/c78dd8f5e9e60206ff7323d29c98cf0e7f0c6063.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a = -b$\" width=\"56\" height=\"12\" /> or <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/e/f/2/ef25218cecd98693b22cf8d8ea33115fbd6920be.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a^2 + b^2 + a - b = 0$\" style=\"vertical-align: -1px\" width=\"149\" height=\"16\" />.  We can divide into two cases.\n</p><p><b>Case 1: <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/c/7/8/c78dd8f5e9e60206ff7323d29c98cf0e7f0c6063.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a = -b$\" width=\"56\" height=\"12\" /></b>\n</p><p>Substituting back results in <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/b/7/f/b7f8fd02d419cbe0d65b7d2ac739f7047ee99508.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\sin{x} = -\\cos{x}$\" width=\"114\" height=\"12\" />.  Since both sides don't equal each other when <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/1/6/7/167122bc6bf807f0b57de7281b0dfbbd9d11e6fc.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\cos{x} = 0$\" width=\"70\" height=\"12\" />, we can divide both sides by <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/3/c/9/3c9cfae39cb378f17672726fb1de7705b94a6da4.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\cos{x}$\" width=\"37\" height=\"8\" /> to get <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/5/b/1/5b1c9de7ca39b763025505eb37ff5a0781810c7c.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\tan{x} = -1$\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px\" width=\"86\" height=\"12\" />.  Thus, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/5/3/1/531cc09ed0c117f77dffc5c00f71640f3a9e9e2e.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x = \\frac{3 \\pi}{4} + \\pi n$\" style=\"vertical-align: -13px\" width=\"102\" height=\"38\" />, where <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/1/7/4/174fadd07fd54c9afe288e96558c92e0c1da733a.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$n$\" width=\"10\" height=\"8\" /> is an integer.\n</p><p><b>Case 2: <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/e/f/2/ef25218cecd98693b22cf8d8ea33115fbd6920be.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a^2 + b^2 + a - b = 0$\" style=\"vertical-align: -1px\" width=\"149\" height=\"16\" /></b>\n</p><p>Substituting back and applying a Pythagorean Identity results in <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/c/c/6/cc6f68d095d6bb1e85adb81bc4bf7ea1cbd08529.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$1 + \\sin{x} - \\cos{x} = 0$\" style=\"vertical-align: -1px\" width=\"160\" height=\"14\" />.  Multiplying both sides by <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/c/c/7/cc7c4b51e06b26289d792878cbf9efac28aac903.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2}$\" style=\"vertical-align: -12px\" width=\"26\" height=\"41\" /> and rearranging results in\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/e/9/c/e9c83a724b2fd7ba6125b9aa972a5fbcf5afa7b6.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\begin{align*} \\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2} &amp;= \\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2} \\cos{x} - \\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2} \\sin{x} \\\\ \\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2} &amp;= \\cos{(x + \\frac{\\pi}{4})} \\end{align*}\" width=\"208\" height=\"89\" />\nFrom the equation, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/a/2/8/a28a330fdfb381bb4962e3323dd46a3b37ab1be6.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x = 0+ 2\\pi n$\" style=\"vertical-align: -2px\" width=\"99\" height=\"15\" /> or <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/8/2/d/82d285ca69b8e6f66f3e266136cac7f86a6a9ea5.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x = \\frac{3 \\pi}{2} + 2\\pi n$\" style=\"vertical-align: -12px\" width=\"111\" height=\"37\" />, where <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/1/7/4/174fadd07fd54c9afe288e96558c92e0c1da733a.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$n$\" width=\"10\" height=\"8\" /> is an integer.  However, both are <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/Extraneous_solutions\" title=\"Extraneous solutions\">extraneous solutions</a> because both make either <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/5/9/3/593e5c9451474d29ad13abf25283cebf82fd6d48.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\tan{x}$\" width=\"39\" height=\"11\" /> or <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/2/1/a/21a2636c4be63386db283774c7d6e14cd0edae11.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\cot{x}$\" width=\"37\" height=\"11\" /> undefined, so there are no solutions in the case.\n</p><p>Therefore the solutions to the equation are <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/f/a/d/fada46ef2b403b3a4c0c1419b46a26fbeb8613c5.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\boxed{x = \\frac{3 \\pi}{4} + \\pi n, n \\in \\mathbb{Z}}$\" style=\"vertical-align: -18px\" width=\"167\" height=\"48\" />.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_Also\">See Also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: See Also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"clear:both; margin:0.5em auto; font-size:95%; border:1px solid black;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"background:#ccf;text-align:center;\" colspan=\"3\"><b><a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_Pan_African_MO\" title=\"2000 Pan African MO\">2000 Pan African MO</a></b> (<b><a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems\" title=\"2000 Pan African MO Problems\">Problems</a></b>)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"33%\" align=\"center\">Preceded&#160;by<br /><b>First Problem</b>\n</td>\n<td width=\"34%\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">1</a> <b>•</b> <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_2\" title=\"2000 Pan African MO Problems/Problem 2\">2</a> <b>•</b> <a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_3&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"2000 Pan African MO Problems/Problem 3 (page does not exist)\">3</a> <b>•</b> <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_4\" title=\"2000 Pan African MO Problems/Problem 4\">4</a> <b>•</b> <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_5\" title=\"2000 Pan African MO Problems/Problem 5\">5</a> <b>•</b> <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_6\" title=\"2000 Pan African MO Problems/Problem 6\">6</a>\n</td>\n<td width=\"33%\" align=\"center\" rowspan=\"1\">Followed&#160;by<br /><b><a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_2\" title=\"2000 Pan African MO Problems/Problem 2\">Problem 2</a></b>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\" colspan=\"3\"><b><a href=\"/wiki/index.php/Pan_African_MO_Problems_and_Solutions\" title=\"Pan African MO Problems and Solutions\"> All Pan African MO Problems and Solutions</a></b>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>[[Category:Introductory Trigonometry Problems]\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240907211132\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.031 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.034 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 250/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 643/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 923/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 51/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4455/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    1.693      1 Template:Pan_African_MO_box\n100.00%    1.693      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wiki-wiki_:pcache:idhash:17899-0!canonical and timestamp 20240907211132 and revision id 190153\n -->\n"
