      "title": "2000 Pan African MO Problems/Problem 2",
      "pageid": 17912,
      "revid": 112854,
      "text": {
        "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Problem\">Problem</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_2&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Problem\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Define the polynomials <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/0/6/f/06f9f506fd37d2c20519f2aa1e6e64530604f4bc.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$P_0, P_1, P_2 \\cdots$\" style=\"vertical-align: -3px\" width=\"96\" height=\"16\" /> by:\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/5/b/1/5b14812d14e0e33eeeebcee5d710289c818e8f26.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\[P_0(x)=x^3+213x^2-67x-2000\\]\" width=\"261\" height=\"19\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/7/b/1/7b139439454d86b7e6509dd4b9c7c982fa295206.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\[P_n(x)=P_{n-1}(x-n), n \\in N\\]\" width=\"222\" height=\"18\" />\nFind the coefficient of <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/2/6/e/26eeb5258ca5099acf8fe96b2a1049c48c89a5e6.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x$\" style=\"vertical-align: -1px\" width=\"12\" height=\"10\" /> in <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/1/8/d/18dedd2db531b1c1d2ab93dda470ffb53d079170.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$P_{21}(x)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -4px\" width=\"48\" height=\"18\" />.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Solution\">Solution</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_2&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Solution\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Note that <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/6/f/1/6f182803090e8d65d636d2d8baf7c2c6170921b8.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$P_1(x) = P_0(x-1)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -4px\" width=\"141\" height=\"18\" />, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/e/a/b/eabed2755b10547af82b1d54c455760b299f50bb.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$P_2(x) = P_1(x-2) = P_0(x-3)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -4px\" width=\"240\" height=\"18\" />, and <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/6/2/f/62f6b788d2d2319566ce19ea4a0c19b9cea356c3.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$P_3(x) = P_2(x-3) = P_1(x-5) = P_0(x-6)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -4px\" width=\"339\" height=\"18\" />.  Thus, we can suspect that <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/e/5/3/e5300183a17cd9ed8261032f45bffdf2d5e29af3.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$P_n(x) = P_0(x - \\tfrac{n(n+1)}{2})$\" style=\"vertical-align: -6px\" width=\"181\" height=\"23\" /> and use <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/Induction\" title=\"Induction\">induction</a> to prove it.\n</p><p>The base case works because <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/e/0/e/e0e18b8f034dfb7437f399ddaed5837d593e4562.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$P_1(x) = P_0(x - \\tfrac{1 \\cdot 2}{2}) = P_0(x-1)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -6px\" width=\"252\" height=\"21\" />.  For the inductive step, assume that <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/e/5/3/e5300183a17cd9ed8261032f45bffdf2d5e29af3.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$P_n(x) = P_0(x - \\tfrac{n(n+1)}{2})$\" style=\"vertical-align: -6px\" width=\"181\" height=\"23\" />.  Thus, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/d/b/a/dbaa9e08cecd9d55b6f6046a4cc6eaac6fcf964f.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\begin{align*} P_n(x - (n+1)) &amp;= P_0(x - (n+1) - \\tfrac{n(n+1)}{2}) \\\\ P_{n+1}(x) &amp;= P_0(x - \\tfrac{(n+1)(n+2)}{2}) \\end{align*}\" width=\"338\" height=\"53\" />\n</p><p>Therefore, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/e/5/3/e5300183a17cd9ed8261032f45bffdf2d5e29af3.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$P_n(x) = P_0(x - \\tfrac{n(n+1)}{2})$\" style=\"vertical-align: -6px\" width=\"181\" height=\"23\" />, so\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/3/5/0/35032807f1a031f76cd4f982e2aa9b9712fbdacf.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\begin{align*} P_{21}(x) &amp;= P_0(x - 21 \\cdot 11) \\\\ &amp;= P_0(x-231) \\\\ &amp;= (x-231)^3 + 213(x-231)^2 - 67(x-231) - 2000 \\end{align*}\" width=\"458\" height=\"70\" />\n</p><p>To find the coefficient of <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/2/6/e/26eeb5258ca5099acf8fe96b2a1049c48c89a5e6.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x$\" style=\"vertical-align: -1px\" width=\"12\" height=\"10\" />, we can use the <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/Binomial_Theorem\" title=\"Binomial Theorem\">Binomial Theorem</a>.  The coefficient of <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/2/6/e/26eeb5258ca5099acf8fe96b2a1049c48c89a5e6.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x$\" style=\"vertical-align: -1px\" width=\"12\" height=\"10\" /> is\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/5/8/1/581b3c2d74254ed815dfa2fbeff13a2458065821.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\[3 \\cdot 231^2 + 213 \\cdot 2 \\cdot -231 - 67\\]\" width=\"223\" height=\"16\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/8/8/b/88bc91caa868256c9084065d1a57a1201480548d.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\[231(231 \\cdot 3 - 426) - 67\\]\" width=\"180\" height=\"18\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/6/8/f/68f920f7c4e57f0c1c0642f43bed87106f3247f0.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\[231(693-426)-67\\]\" width=\"158\" height=\"18\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/b/3/2/b32982d201c642fcc3c4b169387ca6d73d63f251.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\[231(267)-67\\]\" width=\"108\" height=\"18\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/f/6/4/f64fed7fddb49bfb871819ca1e4782f346a33917.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\[\\boxed{61610}\\]\" width=\"57\" height=\"23\" />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_Also\">See Also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_2&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: See Also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"clear:both; margin:0.5em auto; font-size:95%; border:1px solid black;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"background:#ccf;text-align:center;\" colspan=\"3\"><b><a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_Pan_African_MO\" title=\"2000 Pan African MO\">2000 Pan African MO</a></b> (<b><a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems\" title=\"2000 Pan African MO Problems\">Problems</a></b>)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"33%\" align=\"center\">Preceded&#160;by<br /><b><a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_1\" title=\"2000 Pan African MO Problems/Problem 1\">Problem 1</a></b>\n</td>\n<td width=\"34%\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_1\" title=\"2000 Pan African MO Problems/Problem 1\">1</a> <b>•</b> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">2</a> <b>•</b> <a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_3&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"2000 Pan African MO Problems/Problem 3 (page does not exist)\">3</a> <b>•</b> <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_4\" title=\"2000 Pan African MO Problems/Problem 4\">4</a> <b>•</b> <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_5\" title=\"2000 Pan African MO Problems/Problem 5\">5</a> <b>•</b> <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_6\" title=\"2000 Pan African MO Problems/Problem 6\">6</a>\n</td>\n<td width=\"33%\" align=\"center\" rowspan=\"1\">Followed&#160;by<br /><b><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2000_Pan_African_MO_Problems/Problem_3&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"2000 Pan African MO Problems/Problem 3 (page does not exist)\">Problem 3</a></b>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\" colspan=\"3\"><b><a href=\"/wiki/index.php/Pan_African_MO_Problems_and_Solutions\" title=\"Pan African MO Problems and Solutions\"> All Pan African MO Problems and Solutions</a></b>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report